<span class="red">(Mandatory fields)</span></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Choose an interval.
The changes made during this time period will be retrieved.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Data record</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">What type of data do you want to retrieve?
Enter a keyword into this field, e.g. item, order, barcode, sales price etc.</p>
<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Tip</em></strong>: Simply enter the first few letters of the keyword and then use the auto-complete function.</p></td>
