</div>
<h4 id="700" class="discrete">Checking the work of a new employee</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Imagine you’re training a new employee.
Today you gave him the task of updating several old product descriptions.
At the end of the day, you want to make sure he did the job correctly and you want to fix any potential mistakes.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The new employee has a user account with the ID 17.
You could set the search filters as follows:</p>
</div>
