<p>The search results list all of the changes that the employee made today.
Expand a line in the results (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right  "></i></span>) to see more detailed information.
For example:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>what was the text before and after the change?</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>did the employee make a mistake?
Simply click on the link to open the item data record and directly fix the problem.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
