<div class="openblock collapseBox">
<div class="title"><strong>Why don’t I see the menu?</strong></div>
<div class="content">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>People with <a href="/en/business-decisions/user-accounts-access#10">back end access rights</a> can only see this menu if an admin gave them access.</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Find someone who has administrator rights for the plentymarkets system.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>This person will need to open the menu <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Rights » User</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Then he or she will open your user account and activate the necessary rights.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>If the problem continues to exist, contact our <a href="https://forum.plentymarkets.com/c/aenderungshistorie/604" target="_blank" rel="noopener">supporters in the forum</a>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
